on of the network states, we propose a quantum network\nconfiguration protocol, where entanglement purification is used to establish\nhigh-fidelity states. The latter also allows one to show that the entanglement\ngenerated among clients is private, i.e. the network is secure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Nov 2017 16:52:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Jul 2018 11:58:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-09"}
