akness of the relationship persists over a range\nof heliocentric distances. If the correlation is found to strengthen when\ncloser to the Sun, then this would indicate an initial relationship which is\nbeing degraded, perhaps by wave-particle interactions, en route to the observer\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Nov 2017 11:09:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-29"}
